  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Children of 6 month to &lt;36 month of age in good health as determined by medical
             history, physical assessment and clinical judgement of the investigator.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of serious disease. History of serious reaction following administration of
             vaccine or hypersensitivity to vaccine components. Known or suspected
             impairment/alteration of immune function.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
